name: The CMS Roles Search page supports searching for Roles details
fullName: tests/features/search.feature#The CMS Roles Search page supports searching for Roles details

steps.name: Given I am logged into the CMS application
When I click the "DataManagementMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "CompanyManagementMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "RolesMenu" on the "homePage" Page
Then I verify that the "Roles" page is displayed under "companiesPage"
When I navigate to search page
Then I Verify "Search Roles" page is available
And I log out from the CMS application
